content:
Have I told you about the SCP-055 Paradox?
[[>]]
What now?
[[/>]]
Well, one day a researcher said that SCP-055 is the most powerful antimeme in the universe.
[[>]]
Ok, and then?
[[/>]]
How something that can be remembered could be the most powerful antimeme in the universe?
[[>]]
...
[[/>]]
There are more powerful antimemes that no one can remember, right?
[[>]]
I mean, I guess so.
[[/>]]
Like [[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]HESTALKINGABOUTME[[/span]].
[[>]]
Who?
[[/>]]
You know, SCP-[[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]6688[[/span]].
[[>]]
Wait, we have a [[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]6688[[/span]]?
[[/>]]
Shit...
[[>]]
What happened? You look like you saw a ghost.
[[/>]]
Shit, shit, shit, shit...
[[>]]
Stop running, [[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]|/\/|![[/span]] Hey!
[[/>]]
I shouldn't remember about that.
[[>]]
Man, you should see Doctor [[span style="color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 7px rgba(0,0,0,.5)"]]|_/\/\[[/span]], you don't look well.
[[/>]]
